7 An Act relating to environment and natural resources;
7 prohibiting certain actions relating to weather
8 modification; establishing penalty; repealing 82 O.S.
8 2021, Sections 1087.1, 1087.2, 1087.3, 1087.4,
9 1087.5, 1087.6, 1087.7, 1087.8, 1087.9, 1087.10,
9 1087.11, 1087.12, 1087.13, 1087.14, 1087.15, 1087.16,
10 1087.17, 1087.18, 1087.19, 1087.20, 1801.1, 1801.2,
10 and 1801.4, which relate to the Oklahoma Weather
11 Modification Act; providing for codification; and
11 providing an effective date.
12
12
13
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2-5-131 of Title 27A, unless
16
17 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17
18 A. The intentional injection, release, or dispersion, by any
18
19 means, of chemicals, chemical compounds, substances, or apparatus
19
20 within the borders of this state into the atmosphere with express
20
21 purpose of affecting temperature, weather, or the intensity of
21
22 sunlight is prohibited.
22
23
23
24
24
