1 B. Any person convicted of a violation of this section shall be
1
2 guilty of a misdemeanor in the first degree and shall be punished by
2
3 a fine not to exceed Ten Thousand Dollars ($10,000.00).
3
4 SECTION 2. REPEALER 82 O.S. 2021, Sections 1087.1,
4
5 1087.2, 1087.3, 1087.4, 1087.5, 1087.6, 1087.7, 1087.8, 1087.9,
5
6 1087.10, 1087.11, 1087.12, 1087.13, 1087.14, 1087.15, 1087.16,
6
7 1087.17, 1087.18, 1087.19, 1087.20, 1801.1, 1801.2, and 1801.4, are
7
8 hereby repealed.
8
9 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
